text: Michał Jan Żebrowski (born 17 June 1972) is a Polish actor and dramatist. He owns the theater 6 Piętro. Żebrowski was born in Warsaw, Poland. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Polish movie directors Category:Polish screenwriters Category:Polish movie actors Category:Polish playwrights Category:Actors from Warsaw
